title: Patch 5.6 - Cannot accept EULA, Game wont launch
body:
When I boot up the launcher, it updates. then when i click "Launch", the EULA comes up about 5 minutes later, then when I click accept, the EULA disappears, and the second one doesn't show up at all..

I need help, because it wont let me play T_T

Images:
http://prntscr.com/6ljhdm

***LOG FILE: LoLPatcher.log*** - http://pastebin.com/GW9YresU


***LOG FILE: launcher.log*** - http://pastebin.com/HYtx5UNb

replies.body:
The boards supports uploading of screenshots directly to the boards. Click the little paper-clip icon to do that.

Are you on Mac or Windows? Who's your ISP?

I have this issue as well, It happens after every update and has been happening since the DJ Sona patch. I have no idea on how to fix this. If keep spamming launch; nothing. If I wait then also nothing. I really do not understand. It's happening to me right now with the Tahm Kench update. I cannot accept EULA at all. It does pop up and then I accept it then another one appears and I also accept it, and it keeps going like that for hours. Even reinstalling did not fix this issue, so I'm afraid it has to be something with my computer but I cannot figure out what it is.
